</emphasis>
(
<collectingRegion box="[409,589,517,541]" country="Vietnam" name="Lang Son" pageId="7" pageNumber="32">Lang Son province</collectingRegion>
, Huu Lung district, territory of Huu Lien nature reserve). Endemic of limestone areas of northern Vietnam.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
